data.description: This move-in-ready 3-bedroom home on a half-acre lot offers spacious living areas, a sunroom, and a 2-car garage. Recent renovations include fresh flooring, paint, fixtures, and updated kitchen and bath features. The property boasts a large laundry room, an attached side garage, a sizable basement, and a potential attic bonus space. A privacy fence surrounds the backyard with a shed, and there are enclosed porches in both the front and back. This home is a fantastic opportunity for comfortable living with modern updates.
